buyerAgent.name: Shelly Salas Your Home Sold Guaranteed

data.description: NO MORTGAGE PAYMENTS UNTIL APRIL 2024 & SELLER WILL PAY CLOSING COSTS!! Brand new roof!! StyleCraft builders left no stone unturned with the creation of this stunning home. Located in the sought-after subdivision of Yowell Ranch with the glorious community pool so close that it can be seen from the backyard, this Texas-sized house is ready to be made into a home.  As you enter on the right is a grand formal dining room, complete the crown molding, that flows directly into the kitchen, a second dining and a stately living room. The highlight of the expansive living room is a striking fireplace. For added privacy, on the main floor is also where the premiere suite can be found on the opposite side of the home. Upstairs features a large loft, three more sizable bedrooms, and an exceptional theater room! Mature trees offer plenty of shade in the backyard, coupled with an enticing covered patio. There are countless possibilities for the endless space in this home! This gem is a short 15 minute drive to Fort Cavazos and 45 minutes from sensational shopping at the Round Rock Premium outlets! 9408 Glynhill awaits your presence…
